21. It has been generally believed that all the inferior MSS. have come down from the recension of Nicaeus, but that P goes back to a purer source. Biicheler, however, thinks that 311 existing MSS. have come from a codex of the Nicaean recension, containing many variants, and that copyists followed sometimes the text and sometimes the variants.
